text: Mirandaphera arafurensis is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== * Verhecken, A., 1997. Mollusca Gastropoda: Arafura Sea Cancellariidae collected during the Karubar Cruise. Mémoires du Muséum national d'Histoire naturelle 172: 295–323 ==External links== * Holotype in MNHN, Paris Category:Cancellariidae Category:Gastropods described in 1997
title: Mirandaphera arafurensis
